<wingedwarrior41@h...> wrote:
> > "Good luck, old friend," Empath says softly, knowing Maxima won't 
> > hear her.  The femme heads back to the others.  "Let her go.  She 
> > won't cause any trouble."
> 
> Blackfang looked at Empath in a puzzled way.
> 
> Blackfang: All right, if you say so, I guess. Can I count on you to
> keep an eye on her though? I don't want her to get in any kind of
> troubles.

"Of course," Empath laughs.  "I can sense her wherever she goes, just 
like anyone else.  However, right now I have another concern which 
also needs attending to."  Transforming to robot mode, she walks over 
to Windlord.  "Would you mind accompanying me on a little trip, 
honey?"
